#

Caramel Pecan Waffles

30 min
$12.99
450 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

nutsglutendairy

Dietary Tags:

vegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

breakfastbrunchdessert

Description

Fluffy waffles topped with rich caramel sauce and crunchy pecans, perfect for a delightful breakfast or brunch.

Ingredients

  • waffle mix: 2 cups
  • water: 1 3/4 cups
  • pecans: 1/2 cup, chopped
  • caramel sauce: 1/2 cup
  • butter: 2 tablespoons
  • maple syrup: for serving
  • powdered sugar: for dusting
